text.section:
Subject to other provisions of this subtitle, a campaign finance entity shall file campaign finance reports as follows:
except for a ballot issue committee, on or before the fourth Tuesday immediately preceding each primary election except a presidential primary election;
except for a ballot issue committee, on or before the second Friday immediately preceding a primary election;
for a ballot issue committee only, on or before the fourth Friday immediately preceding a general election;
on or before the second Friday immediately preceding a general election; and
on or before the third Tuesday after a general election.
